  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DATA ROT</strong> is an ominous Virtual Reality horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the last line of defense. An insidious <i>Daemon </i>is taking control of your system.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/1755824de8d4806fe51a0810c35c1a88.poster.avif?t=1748618577\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/1755824de8d4806fe51a0810c35c1a88.webm?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/1755824de8d4806fe51a0810c35c1a88.mp4?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the 8 scattered <i>Data Fragments</i> to eliminate the <i>Daemon</i> before it corrupts the mainframe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/f0b43ced8561a4bee2831bfd7077bb0f.poster.avif?t=1748618577\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/f0b43ced8561a4bee2831bfd7077bb0f.webm?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/f0b43ced8561a4bee2831bfd7077bb0f.mp4?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the corrupted remains of a once-thriving system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/7bf47e174e4a72c4b40a832a405242ef.poster.avif?t=1748618577\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/7bf47e174e4a72c4b40a832a405242ef.webm?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/7bf47e174e4a72c4b40a832a405242ef.mp4?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the corruption spreads and the <i>Daemon</i> takes control, the world devolves around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/6bd17e7f6853228124fde8443b642c70.poster.avif?t=1748618577\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/6bd17e7f6853228124fde8443b642c70.webm?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/6bd17e7f6853228124fde8443b642c70.mp4?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive at all costs! Don't let the <i>Daemon</i> catch you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/0d8014810b4ec6c5fadfa30a0cbf2f4b.poster.avif?t=1748618577\" width=434 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/0d8014810b4ec6c5fadfa30a0cbf2f4b.webm?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3738180/extras/0d8014810b4ec6c5fadfa30a0cbf2f4b.mp4?t=1748618577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20-45 minute playthrough</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Intuitive, addictive gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Dynamic AI Opponent that hunts  the player</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Roomscale or Seated experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Retro-futuristic ASCII style</p>",
